snippet.title: Kung Fu Panda 2: Official Video Game Trailer
snippet.description:
Kung Fu Panda 2 the video game - http://bit.ly/Kung-Fu-Panda-2-Video-Game  

Hey, Kung Fu Panda fans! Get ready for the Kung Fu Panda 2 video game,  available May 24 for Xbox360 for Kinect, PlayStation 3, Wii GameTablet and Nintendo DS. Make sure to visit http://www.kungfupanda2videogame.com  for a sneak peak of Po's new adventures.
